The paper discusses learning to transform filters for use in group convolutions, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper mentions achieving high performance on image classification tasks, which suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also mentions low sensitivity to input rotations, which could be related to natural language processing (cs.CL) in addition to computer vision.
